load_tweets() - Method in class tri
Loads each line of the csv file into one long string variable called score The string is then split by only commas outside of quotes to give us the 6 columns index 0 is the tweets score, index 6 is the tweet itself from the csv file The score for each tweet is loaded into a list called target, and the tweets is loaded into a list called tweets.
